00:24:56,760 --> 00:24:57,680
What do I gain from this?

578
00:24:57,680 --> 00:24:58,760
I'm trying to help you both solve a problem.

579
00:24:58,760 --> 00:24:59,520
Why are you yelling here?

580
00:24:59,520 --> 00:25:00,160
You're so frustrating.

581
00:25:00,160 --> 00:25:01,560
I still have to save you, after all.

582
00:25:01,560 --> 00:25:02,520
There aren't enough beds for everyone.

583
00:25:02,520 --> 00:25:03,960
You should go back and check on your child.

584
00:25:03,960 --> 00:25:05,000
Buy two cans of food for the child.

585
00:25:05,000 --> 00:25:06,960
Let me pay for it, okay?

586
00:25:06,960 --> 00:25:09,520
Alright.

587
00:25:10,280 --> 00:25:11,520
He's just a scumbag.

588
00:25:11,520 --> 00:25:13,520
That's enough. Don't scare the lady.

589
00:25:13,520 --> 00:25:14,520
She just had surgery.

590
00:25:14,520 --> 00:25:15,720
You need to go back to bed.

591
00:25:15,720 --> 00:25:17,980
Your incision might reopen. Go back now.

592
00:25:23,000 --> 00:25:25,000
As early as March last year,

593
00:25:25,720 --> 00:25:27,480
authoritative overseas media

594
00:25:28,000 --> 00:25:29,040
reported on

595
00:25:29,280 --> 00:25:30,800
these pinhole glasses.

596
00:25:31,440 --> 00:25:33,100
It doesn't cure myopia at all.

597
00:25:33,280 --> 00:25:35,340
What are you all doing with your jobs?

598
00:25:35,520 --> 00:25:38,650
Letting such a useless thing become popular in schools.

599
00:25:38,760 --> 00:25:39,960
Many students

600
00:25:40,760 --> 00:25:41,560
are in class

601
00:25:42,320 --> 00:25:44,320
and sleeping with these glasses on.

602
00:25:44,520 --> 00:25:46,280
Teachers can't even notice it.

603
00:25:46,720 --> 00:25:47,720
What's worse,

604
00:25:48,600 --> 00:25:51,320
the unscrupulous distributor of these glasses

605
00:25:51,320 --> 00:25:52,280
has even organized

606
00:25:52,280 --> 00:25:54,440
some kind of student distributor conference.

607
00:25:54,440 --> 00:25:56,240
They caused a 10-year-old child

608
00:25:56,480 --> 00:25:57,880
to end up in the hospital.

609
00:25:58,000 --> 00:25:59,040
Ten years old!

610
00:25:59,040 --> 00:26:00,000
Just ten!

611
00:26:00,360 --> 00:26:03,800
Industry, tax, and police authorities are now conducting joint enforcement.

612
00:26:03,800 --> 00:26:05,260
Investigate thoroughly.

613
00:26:20,080 --> 00:26:21,210
Is Cui Guoming home?

614
00:26:23,520 --> 00:26:24,520
Yes.

615
00:26:30,280 --> 00:26:31,810
You're Cui Guoming, right?

616
00:26:33,600 --> 00:26:34,200
Please have a seat.

617
00:26:34,200 --> 00:26:35,520
I'll make some tea for you.

618
00:26:35,520 --> 00:26:36,680
We won't sit down.

619
00:26:37,000 --> 00:26:37,480
It's like this.

620
00:26:37,480 --> 00:26:38,920
Get changed now

621
00:26:39,280 --> 00:26:40,240
and come with us.

622
00:26:40,320 --> 00:26:41,440
There are some matters

623
00:26:41,440 --> 00:26:42,970
we need to discuss with you.

624
00:26:44,280 --> 00:26:45,600
Can't we verify it here?

625
00:26:45,600 --> 00:26:46,600
This is a summons.

626
00:26:46,960 --> 00:26:49,280
You need to come with us.

627
00:26:49,280 --> 00:26:51,000
If you don't understand what a summons is,

628
00:26:51,000 --> 00:26:52,480
I can explain it to you right now.

629
00:26:52,480 --> 00:26:53,000
No need.

630
00:26:53,520 --> 00:26:53,800
That won't be necessary.

631
00:26:53,800 --> 00:26:55,530
I'll go change my clothes then.

632
00:26:58,280 --> 00:26:59,360
I'll change. You all...

633
00:26:59,360 --> 00:27:01,000
Don't panic, okay?

634
00:27:06,360 --> 00:27:09,000
Sir, please don't take my father away.

635
00:27:09,240 --> 00:27:10,480
You all be good now.

636
00:27:10,480 --> 00:27:12,610
Don't worry. Everything will be fine.

637
00:27:13,440 --> 00:27:15,160
Please don't take my father away.

638
00:27:15,160 --> 00:27:16,480
My father is a good man.

639
00:27:16,560 --> 00:27:17,480
He's just unreliable.

640
00:27:17,480 --> 00:27:19,080
He wouldn't do anything bad.

641
00:27:22,080 --> 00:27:23,740
Why are you dressed so nicely?

642
00:27:24,920 --> 00:27:28,320
Isn't this out of respect for you all? What's wrong with that?

643
00:27:29,240 --> 00:27:29,320
I suggest you...

644
00:27:29,320 --> 00:27:29,800
I suggest you

645
00:27:29,800 --> 00:27:31,860
change into something more worn out.

646
00:27:32,320 --> 00:27:33,160
Why?

647
00:27:33,200 --> 00:27:35,560
You look like an educated man.

648
00:27:35,720 --> 00:27:37,360
With your scholarly appearance,

649
00:27:37,360 --> 00:27:39,020
if you wear these nice clothes

650
00:27:39,040 --> 00:27:40,520
when you go into the detention center,

651
00:27:40,520 --> 00:27:42,280
those inmates will surely

652
00:27:42,360 --> 00:27:43,560
take them from you.

653
00:27:44,720 --> 00:27:47,250
Do I really have to go to the detention center?

654
00:27:50,720 --> 00:27:51,200
Alright.

655
00:27:51,200 --> 00:27:52,160
After your aunt comes back,

656
00:27:52,160 --> 00:27:54,360
take her to Guo Xiaoxue's home.

657
00:27:54,360 --> 00:27:55,520
Check on her and her grandfather.

658
00:27:55,520 --> 00:27:57,160
I don't know when I'll be released.

659
00:27:57,160 --> 00:27:58,480
I'm worried they might not have enough money.

660
00:27:58,480 --> 00:27:59,340
Remember that.

661
00:27:59,720 --> 00:28:00,480
And then,

662
00:28:00,920 --> 00:28:01,600
don't worry about me.

663
00:28:01,600 --> 00:28:02,920
Just go home now.

664
00:28:13,240 --> 00:28:14,320
Coming, coming.

665
00:28:27,320 --> 00:28:28,580
What's wrong with you?

666
00:28:32,440 --> 00:28:33,570
Take this medicine.

667
00:28:34,360 --> 00:28:35,600
Why should I take it?

668
00:28:35,600 --> 00:28:36,560
You must take it.

669
00:28:37,240 --> 00:28:38,560
It's absolutely necessary.

670
00:28:38,560 --> 00:28:40,000
I don't have any symptoms.

671
00:28:40,000 --> 00:28:41,480
Why should I take it?

672
00:28:41,480 --> 00:28:42,520
I'll tell you after you take it.

673
00:28:42,520 --> 00:28:43,800
Go ahead. What is it?

674
00:28:43,840 --> 00:28:44,680
If I tell you now,

675
00:28:44,680 --> 00:28:45,840
taking the medicine afterward will be too late.

676
00:28:45,840 --> 00:28:47,000
Take it first, then I'll tell you.

677
00:28:47,000 --> 00:28:49,200
Uh, you tell me first, then I'll take it.

678
00:28:49,440 --> 00:28:51,500
If you don't take it, I won't tell you.

679
00:29:01,600 --> 00:29:02,440
I've taken it.

680
00:29:03,000 --> 00:29:03,680
Now tell me.

681
00:29:03,680 --> 00:29:04,800
Wait three minutes.

682
00:29:04,800 --> 00:29:06,240
The medicine hasn't taken effect yet.

683
00:29:06,240 --> 00:29:06,680
Look,

684
00:29:06,760 --> 00:29:07,680
if you don't tell me soon,

685
00:29:07,680 --> 00:29:10,010
I'm going to have a heart attack right now.

686
00:29:10,800 --> 00:29:12,760
Then I'll tell you the good news first.

687
00:29:12,760 --> 00:29:14,160
You'd better tell me the bad news first.

688
00:29:14,160 --> 00:29:15,440
No, the medicine hasn't taken effect yet.

689
00:29:15,440 --> 00:29:16,600
I'll tell you the good news first.

690
00:29:16,600 --> 00:29:18,400
Guoming passed the lawyer exam.

691
00:29:18,600 --> 00:29:20,120
There's nothing special about that.

692
00:29:20,120 --> 00:29:21,920
Of course he's good at studying.

693
00:29:22,120 --> 00:29:24,280
That's not really good news.

694
00:29:24,280 --> 00:29:25,880
Just tell me the bad news now.

695
00:29:26,320 --> 00:29:28,320
Guoming has been arrested by the police.

696
00:29:28,320 --> 00:29:29,280
What?

697
00:29:31,280 --> 00:29:31,640
Dad.

698
00:29:32,120 --> 00:29:33,120
I said the medicine hasn't taken effect yet.

699
00:29:33,120 --> 00:29:34,650
But you insisted I tell you.

700
00:29:34,880 --> 00:29:36,880
What for?

701
00:29:37,120 --> 00:29:39,720
Because pinhole glasses are classified as medical devices.

702
00:29:39,720 --> 00:29:41,800
Guoming was manufacturing them illegally.

703
00:29:41,800 --> 00:29:43,760
He wasn't just illegally manufacturing and selling them.

704
00:29:43,760 --> 00:29:45,440
He was also evading taxes.

705
00:29:45,760 --> 00:29:47,620
And allegedly employing minors.

706
00:29:55,720 --> 00:29:56,480
Director,

707
00:29:57,280 --> 00:29:59,280
guess what happened to Cui Guoming?

708
00:30:00,440 --> 00:30:02,480
No guessing, I won't make you guess.

709
00:30:03,600 --> 00:30:04,480
Little Cui

710
00:30:04,480 --> 00:30:06,560
has been arrested by the police again.

711
00:30:06,560 --> 00:30:08,680
Wasn't he making those pinhole glasses

712
00:30:08,680 --> 00:30:09,880
and doing quite well?

713
00:30:09,880 --> 00:30:11,320
It's exactly about those pinhole glasses.

714
00:30:11,320 --> 00:30:12,680
I just found out myself.

715
00:30:12,680 --> 00:30:14,040
Producing pinhole glasses

716
00:30:14,040 --> 00:30:15,700
falls under medical devices.

717
00:30:16,080 --> 00:30:18,760
Our Cui is quite talented.

718
00:30:18,760 --> 00:30:21,760
He was manufacturing medical devices without a license.

719
00:30:21,760 --> 00:30:23,880
He definitely hasn't paid a penny in taxes.

720
00:30:23,880 --> 00:30:26,010
Who else should they arrest if not him?

721
00:30:26,160 --> 00:30:27,760
And he even got some kids

722
00:30:27,760 --> 00:30:29,120
to work as his distributors.

723
00:30:29,120 --> 00:30:31,040
What would you call this behavior?

724
00:30:31,040 --> 00:30:33,360
He's like Huang Shiren and Zhou Bapi combined,

725
00:30:33,360 --> 00:30:34,760
a real Hu Hansan!

726
00:30:35,080 --> 00:30:35,880
Wait a minute.

727
00:30:37,320 --> 00:30:39,760
Did Hu Hansan exploit child workers?

728
00:30:41,720 --> 00:30:43,080
It's been so long since I watched that movie,

729
00:30:43,080 --> 00:30:43,880
I've forgotten.

730
00:30:43,880 --> 00:30:45,080
Oh, of course!

731
00:30:45,080 --> 00:30:45,720
Pan Dongzi!

732
00:30:45,720 --> 00:30:46,800
Hu Hansan brutally beats

733
00:30:46,800 --> 00:30:48,160
Pan Dongzi,

734
00:30:48,160 --> 00:30:51,080
that Red Army soldier from 'Sparkling Red Star',

735
00:30:51,360 --> 00:30:52,560
Pan Dongzi.

736
00:30:53,600 --> 00:30:56,480
The red star shines brilliantly,

737
00:30:56,800 --> 00:30:58,160
glowing brightly.

738
00:30:58,240 --> 00:30:59,960
Alright,

739
00:30:59,960 --> 00:31:01,080
enough.

740
00:31:01,080 --> 00:31:03,140
Your skills are no match for Xiao Cui.

741
00:31:03,800 --> 00:31:04,640
Yes,

742
00:31:04,960 --> 00:31:06,960
my singing isn't as good as his,

743
00:31:07,200 --> 00:31:10,320
but my heart is more righteous than his.

744
00:31:11,560 --> 00:31:12,800
Fine.

745
00:31:13,240 --> 00:31:14,840
Why can't you speak straightforwardly?

746
00:31:14,840 --> 00:31:15,840
Go sit over there.

747
00:31:17,280 --> 00:31:18,600
I've been asking around.

748
00:31:18,600 --> 00:31:20,320
For behavior like his,

749
00:31:20,320 --> 00:31:22,120
a fine is

750
00:31:22,120 --> 00:31:23,450
definitely necessary.

751
00:31:24,280 --> 00:31:27,960
But it's at that stage where he might or might not be sentenced.

752
00:31:28,880 --> 00:31:30,920
If we push a bit harder

753
00:31:31,960 --> 00:31:32,800
and find the right connections,

754
00:31:32,800 --> 00:31:34,560
he might just get sentenced.

755
00:31:35,240 --> 00:31:36,680
Well, if

756
00:31:36,680 --> 00:31:37,560
he gets sentenced,

757
00:31:37,560 --> 00:31:39,760
we can fire him directly.

758
00:31:40,200 --> 00:31:42,760
You'll have no choice but to dismiss him,

759
00:31:43,320 --> 00:31:45,920
and it will save our factory tens of thousands.

760
00:31:57,160 --> 00:31:59,320
Director, please stop staring at me.

761
00:31:59,320 --> 00:32:00,640
What do you mean?

762
00:32:03,800 --> 00:32:05,480
What do I mean?

763
00:32:05,880 --> 00:32:07,040
I see you as

764
00:32:07,800 --> 00:32:08,920
Zhao Gao,

765
00:32:09,880 --> 00:32:10,800
Gao Lishi,

766
00:32:11,320 --> 00:32:12,320
Wei Zhongxian.

767
00:32:13,160 --> 00:32:14,120
Li Lianying.

768
00:32:15,440 --> 00:32:17,840
This Xiao Cui may be careless,

769
00:32:17,840 --> 00:32:18,920
showing no respect for hierarchy,

770
00:32:18,920 --> 00:32:20,520
and lacking proper manners.

771
00:32:21,480 --> 00:32:23,840
But after all, he has worked in our company

772
00:32:24,240 --> 00:32:27,080
for over ten years as a veteran employee and colleague.

773
00:32:27,080 --> 00:32:29,160
Don't we have any class solidarity?

774
00:32:32,080 --> 00:32:33,210
He's in trouble now.

775
00:32:34,280 --> 00:32:36,410
It's one thing to wash our hands of him,

776
00:32:36,440 --> 00:32:39,080
because we've wanted to lay him off for a long time.

777
00:32:39,080 --> 00:32:40,440
But at this moment,

778
00:32:41,960 --> 00:32:42,880
if we kick him

779
00:32:43,320 --> 00:32:44,720
when he's down,

780
00:32:45,800 --> 00:32:46,920
if this gets out,

781
00:32:47,800 --> 00:32:50,000
how can I continue as factory director?

782
00:32:50,240 --> 00:32:51,770
How will I command respect?

783
00:32:52,120 --> 00:32:53,240
You're right.

784
00:32:53,240 --> 00:32:55,440
I wasn't thinking as thoroughly as you.

785
00:32:56,320 --> 00:32:58,800
True, I find this Cui quite annoying,

786
00:33:00,360 --> 00:33:02,800
but just keep him out of my sight.

787
00:33:03,320 --> 00:33:06,120
We don't need to go as far as sending him to prison.

788
00:33:13,640 --> 00:33:14,480
After a fair

789
00:33:15,400 --> 00:33:16,860
and just bidding process,

790
00:33:17,240 --> 00:33:18,360
starting today,

791
00:33:18,680 --> 00:33:21,080
I officially take over Dingqing Restaurant.

792
00:33:21,080 --> 00:33:21,940
I hope everyone

793
00:33:22,160 --> 00:33:23,160
will give me your full support.

794
00:33:23,160 --> 00:33:23,880
Support!

795
00:33:26,880 --> 00:33:28,200
Perhaps

796
00:33:28,200 --> 00:33:29,660
some long-time employees

797
00:33:29,840 --> 00:33:31,760
are unhappy about my taking over

798
00:33:32,280 --> 00:33:33,540
Dingqing Restaurant.

799
00:33:34,280 --> 00:33:34,960
But

800
00:33:34,960 --> 00:33:38,280
I've put everything I have into this business.

801
00:33:38,680 --> 00:33:40,840
I scraped together 250,000

802
00:33:41,320 --> 00:33:42,960
It wasn't easy.

803
00:33:43,760 --> 00:33:44,640
to make this happen.

804
00:33:44,640 --> 00:33:45,720
I just want to do a good job

805
00:33:45,720 --> 00:33:48,120
and lead everyone to prosperity together.

806
00:33:48,480 --> 00:33:50,280
The name 'Dingqing Restaurant'

807
00:33:50,560 --> 00:33:53,560
is old-fashioned and outdated.

808
00:33:54,080 --> 00:33:56,840
What young person would like such a name?

809
00:33:58,400 --> 00:34:00,600
I plan to give it a new name,

810
00:34:01,160 --> 00:34:03,280
something more wild,

811
00:34:03,680 --> 00:34:04,720
we'll call it

812
00:34:05,280 --> 00:34:07,560
Wild Rose Dinner and Dance.

813
00:34:07,560 --> 00:34:08,760
What do you all think?

814
00:34:41,600 --> 00:34:43,400
If you're taking over the restaurant,

815
00:34:43,400 --> 00:34:45,130
how much more money do you need?

816
00:34:46,120 --> 00:34:46,920
Sister Zhou,

817
00:34:47,639 --> 00:34:48,840
don't worry about it.

818
00:34:49,639 --> 00:34:51,699
I've saved some money over the years.

819
00:34:52,000 --> 00:34:53,130
You can use it first.

820
00:34:57,960 --> 00:34:59,490
We're quite short on funds.

821
00:35:04,440 --> 00:35:05,500
I have over 30,000.

822
00:35:08,440 --> 00:35:09,770
Thank you, Sister Zhou.

823
00:35:11,480 --> 00:35:12,320
But right now,

824
00:35:13,760 --> 00:35:15,160
it's not about the money.

825
00:35:31,400 --> 00:35:32,930
This is Guo Xiaoxue's home.

826
00:35:36,000 --> 00:35:36,560
Let's go.

827
00:35:36,560 --> 00:35:37,000
Okay.

828
00:35:50,520 --> 00:35:50,980
This...

829
00:35:54,040 --> 00:35:54,840
Who's there?

830
00:35:55,440 --> 00:35:56,360
Huo Xiaoyang.

831
00:36:00,120 --> 00:36:00,800
Guo Xiaoxue.

832
00:36:00,800 --> 00:36:01,760
This is my aunt.

833
00:36:02,120 --> 00:36:03,400
Hello, Aunt.

834
00:36:03,960 --> 00:36:05,240
Are you home alone?

835
00:36:20,760 --> 00:36:21,680
You live here?

836
00:36:30,480 --> 00:36:32,480
Have you been living here all along?

837
00:36:37,040 --> 00:36:38,170
Do we have any brooms

838
00:36:38,280 --> 00:36:39,440
or cleaning cloths?

839
00:36:39,880 --> 00:36:41,280
Let's clean this place up

840
00:36:41,760 --> 00:36:43,220
before we go find Grandpa.

841
00:36:43,680 --> 00:36:44,480
Sure!

842
00:36:45,800 --> 00:36:47,040
Where are they?

843
00:36:47,040 --> 00:36:47,600
Where?

844
00:36:48,360 --> 00:36:48,840
Got it!

845
00:36:52,640 --> 00:36:53,900
It's okay, don't move.

846
00:37:06,120 --> 00:37:07,600
You're not wearing enough.

847
00:37:07,600 --> 00:37:08,160
Here,

848
00:37:10,120 --> 00:37:10,960
put this on.

849
00:37:39,840 --> 00:37:41,440
Your grandfather's name is

850
00:37:41,920 --> 00:37:42,640
Guo Jun

851
00:37:43,040 --> 00:37:43,840
comrade.

852
00:37:43,840 --> 00:37:44,720
Could you please check

853
00:37:44,720 --> 00:37:46,520
how much money is left in Guo Jun's account?

854
00:37:46,520 --> 00:37:47,720
Are you his daughter?

855
00:37:48,040 --> 00:37:48,840
No, I'm not.

856
00:37:49,320 --> 00:37:50,580
His daughter-in-law?

857
00:37:51,160 --> 00:37:53,160
No. I don't know him.

858
00:37:54,680 --> 00:37:55,840
You don't know him?

859
00:37:55,840 --> 00:37:58,040
He's my husband's classmate's father.

860
00:37:59,040 --> 00:38:00,280
Where is your husband's classmate?

861
00:38:00,280 --> 00:38:01,540
Where is your husband?

862
00:38:04,160 --> 00:38:05,880
I brought his granddaughter here.

863
00:38:05,880 --> 00:38:07,140
Please check it for me.

864
00:38:11,720 --> 00:38:13,200
There's still enough for now.

865
00:38:13,200 --> 00:38:14,840
But it's almost gone.

866
00:38:14,920 --> 00:38:15,960
You should prepare

867
00:38:15,960 --> 00:38:17,490
for the upcoming expenses.

868
00:38:19,240 --> 00:38:20,920
How much more will we need?

869
00:38:21,160 --> 00:38:22,690
Prepare 10,000 yuan first.

870
00:38:30,920 --> 00:38:31,720
Let's go.

871
00:38:36,920 --> 00:38:38,000
What's wrong, Dad?

872
00:38:39,520 --> 00:38:41,000
Why are you staring at me?

873
00:38:41,080 --> 00:38:43,210
I'm waiting for you to get my medicine.

874
00:38:43,720 --> 00:38:44,720
No need today.

875
00:38:45,160 --> 00:38:47,490
I just want to discuss something with you.

876
00:38:48,560 --> 00:38:49,720
What is it?

877
00:38:51,080 --> 00:38:51,920
That guy Tang

878
00:38:51,920 --> 00:38:53,000
has gone ahead and

879
00:38:53,000 --> 00:38:54,860
leased the Dingqing Restaurant.

880
00:38:55,200 --> 00:38:56,800
That was inevitable.

881
00:38:57,360 --> 00:38:59,020
I don't want to work under him.

882
00:38:59,440 --> 00:39:01,040
But Guoming is still in jail.

883
00:39:01,200 --> 00:39:02,640
If I don't have a job,

884
00:39:03,360 --> 00:39:05,090
what will happen to our family?

885
00:39:07,000 --> 00:39:08,920
Guoming's lawyer license

886
00:39:08,920 --> 00:39:11,380
hadn't even been issued when this happened.

887
00:39:12,000 --> 00:39:13,400
I've been asking around.

888
00:39:13,560 --> 00:39:15,440
I heard about Guoming's case.

889
00:39:15,440 --> 00:39:18,440
Just confiscating his illegal income isn't enough.

890
00:39:18,560 --> 00:39:20,160
There will be additional fines.

891
00:39:20,160 --> 00:39:22,280
The glasses factory will be shut down.

892
00:39:22,280 --> 00:39:24,440
All those glasses will be destroyed.

893
00:39:24,640 --> 00:39:27,440
He might even get sentenced.

894
00:39:27,440 --> 00:39:28,440
Sentenced?

895
00:39:29,080 --> 00:39:30,640
I said might.

896
00:39:31,920 --> 00:39:34,320
The sentence probably won't be too severe.

897
00:39:34,800 --> 00:39:37,080
At most, he'll get probation.

898
00:39:41,680 --> 00:39:42,540
By the way, Dad.

899
00:39:42,960 --> 00:39:43,960
That Tang guy

900
00:39:44,080 --> 00:39:44,800
wants to take down our

901
00:39:44,800 --> 00:39:46,520
Dingqing Restaurant sign.

902
00:39:46,520 --> 00:39:47,800
He wants to rename it

903
00:39:48,120 --> 00:39:49,880
Wild Rose Song and Dance Restaurant.

904
00:39:49,880 --> 00:39:50,760
The entire second floor

905
00:39:50,760 --> 00:39:52,200
will be turned into small dance halls,

906
00:39:52,200 --> 00:39:53,120
you know, those dimly lit places,

907
00:39:53,120 --> 00:39:53,760
that kind of nightclub.

908
00:39:53,760 --> 00:39:55,040
What did you say?

909
00:39:55,040 --> 00:39:55,880
There must be those

910
00:39:55,880 --> 00:39:57,520
dirty prostitutes and such.

911
00:39:57,520 --> 00:39:58,520
Get the medicine.

912
00:39:58,520 --> 00:39:59,580
Heart pills, okay?

913
00:39:59,960 --> 00:40:01,760
Nitroglycerin.

914
00:40:11,800 --> 00:40:13,920
Brother's here.

915
00:40:16,640 --> 00:40:17,320
No.

916
00:40:17,320 --> 00:40:18,200
You've come in again.

917
00:40:18,200 --> 00:40:19,860
Still haven't been released?

918
00:40:19,920 --> 00:40:21,050
Here you come again.

919
00:40:21,120 --> 00:40:22,360
What do you want from me?

920
00:40:22,360 --> 00:40:23,400
This is a nice place.

921
00:40:23,400 --> 00:40:25,040
You keep coming back again and again.

922
00:40:25,040 --> 00:40:26,200
Let me get some sleep.

923
00:40:26,200 --> 00:40:27,800
I haven't slept for a day and night.

924
00:40:27,800 --> 00:40:29,360
Liuzi, we have guests.

925
00:40:29,360 --> 00:40:31,290
Get two more quilts for your uncle.

926
00:40:31,880 --> 00:40:33,140
Don't fall asleep now.

927
00:40:36,760 --> 00:40:38,520
Cover yourself up.

928
00:40:57,360 --> 00:40:59,040
After our renovation

929
00:40:59,240 --> 00:41:00,320
it'll be absolutely stylish,

930
00:41:00,320 --> 00:41:01,080
totally trendy,

931
00:41:01,080 --> 00:41:02,200
and definitely cool.

932
00:41:02,200 --> 00:41:03,520
We're changing the name to

933
00:41:03,520 --> 00:41:05,680
Wild Rose Dinner and Dance,

934
00:41:05,680 --> 00:41:07,200
not Dingqing Restaurant anymore.

935
00:41:07,200 --> 00:41:08,880
But no matter what we call it,

936
00:41:09,240 --> 00:41:10,080
Mr. Cui,

937
00:41:10,200 --> 00:41:11,260
whenever you come,

938
00:41:11,400 --> 00:41:13,060
it's absolutely on the house.

939
00:41:13,400 --> 00:41:14,800
When it was state-owned,

940
00:41:15,040 --> 00:41:16,120
I didn't have that authority.

941
00:41:16,120 --> 00:41:17,640
Now that I've contracted it,

942
00:41:17,640 --> 00:41:19,300
I definitely have that power.

943
00:41:34,240 --> 00:41:35,520
Be careful.

944
00:41:41,800 --> 00:41:42,920
Manager Tang.

945
00:41:45,000 --> 00:41:47,760
I hired a tricycle.

946
00:41:49,120 --> 00:41:51,880
Could you help carry this old plaque back?

947
00:41:52,440 --> 00:41:53,320
No problem.

948
00:41:53,560 --> 00:41:55,640
What do I need this old thing for?

949
00:41:57,560 --> 00:41:58,320
Sir,

950
00:41:59,680 --> 00:42:01,440
would you mind giving us a hand?

951
00:42:01,440 --> 00:42:02,880
Let me help you carry it.

952
00:42:02,880 --> 00:42:03,680
No need.

953
00:42:07,560 --> 00:42:09,220
If this isn't being stubborn,

954
00:42:09,240 --> 00:42:10,320
then what is?
